components.title: APRA CPS234 - AWS OF the cloud
components.description: Component describing AWS supplier level controls and how they assist in meeting APRA CPS234 and CPG234 Guidance. The controls specified are those that have been identified as belonging to "OF the cloud" in the shared responsibility model.

components.title: SOC2 controls validation
components.description: Component describing independent testing results for AWS supplier level controls.
